Markdown Format Guidelines

    Use # Title for the scenario title (first H1 header)
    Use <!-- CHAPTER_START n: Title --> and <!-- CHAPTER_END --> to define chapters
    Use <!-- READING_START --> and <!-- READING_END --> for reading sections
    Use <!-- QUESTION_START --> and <!-- QUESTION_END --> for questions
    For questions, include:
        Question: [question text]
        Comment: [comment text] (optional)
        Answers: section with multiple answer blocks, each containing:
            Value: [answer value]
            Points: [points for this answer] (optional, defaults to 1)

